ttps://www.facebook.com/enoch.ho.fx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fenoch.ho.fx&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8utE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=0951ece0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/enoch.ho.fx</a><br />\nKwong Wai Ming\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kwong.w.ming\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkwong.w.ming&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8utE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=c057ea58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kwong.w.ming</a><br />\n我諗以上人士都應該唔想去美國，佢哋申請美國簽證申請應該凍過水，因為我懷疑以上人渣係 圈中人 嘅startup戶口群嚟。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 陳澍唔交代都唔緊要，呢單嘢夠晒料證明Facebook Hong Kong and Taiwan同共產黨關係密切，我認為台灣政府同美國政府係時候對Facebook採取行動，甚至應該引用國家安全法律搜查Facecook Server同辦公室，喺我眼中，Zuckerberg真係同賣國賊無分別。<br />\n<br />\n圈中人係乜水，我等Facebook交代清楚，定有公司會刪咗個Page。<br />\n<br />\n(個Page係我用正常Facebook Search搵唔到，我要掃系統先Search，仲要Facebook詭異地block咗我大數據系統嘅data feed，有啲人做緊仆街嘢都好明顯，係Facebook公司全力配合)<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/27161/%e5%9c%88%e4%b8%ad%e4%ba%ba-%e7%99%bb%e5%bb%a3%e5%91%8a%e5%98%85%e8%b3%87%e9%87%91%e9%82%8a%e5%ba%a6%e5%9a%9f%ef%bc%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F27161%2F%25e5%259c%2588%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e4%25ba%25ba-%25e7%2599%25bb%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%2591%258a%25e5%2598%2585%25e8%25b3%2587%25e9%2587%2591%25e9%2582%258a%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%259a%259f%25ef%25bc%259f&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8utE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=09c38bdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/27161/%e5%9c%88%e4%b8%ad%e4%ba%ba-%e7%99%bb%e5%bb%a3%e5%91%8a%e5%98%85%e8%b3%87%e9%87%91%e9%82%8a%e5%ba%a6%e5%9a%9f%ef%bc%9f</a>"},{"pid":"fb9088bdccde59fe6f578d84362780964345f1b0","tid":1190966,"uid":98692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幅圖是咪錯？左下角點解是黃之峰"},{"pid":"64153492d531aa4964561ccecc3ebad515385b36",